item.title: Analysis of COVID-19 cases in Toronto
item.description: Code and data supporting this analysis is available at: “https://github.com/zhoufanx/STA304-Assignment1”. We use R (R Core Team 2020) and packages tidyverse (Wickham et al. 2019), visdat (Tierney 2017), labelled (Larmarange 2020), opendatatoronto (Gelfand 2020), dplyr (Wickham et al. 2020), qwraps2 (DeWitt 2020) for this analysis. Abstract: “We investigate the data about COVID-19 Cases in Toronto. By analyzing, results showed that age group, gender and source of infection distribution of cases and the out come of these Cases.
